  <description><![CDATA[<p>Ideally located in the centre of Sauze d'Oulx, the Hotel K2 offers great service and facilities in a modern alpine setting.</p>
<h3>Central location</h3>
<p>Hotel K2 is located right in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0b1d3c577424320a9af2e1af08b6887}" title="Sauze d'Oulx">Sauze d'Oulx</a> with easy access to all the lively restaurants and bars the resort has to offer. You're just 200 metres from the Clotes chair lift.</p>
<p>A three minute walk away is the <a data-udi="umb://document/2082ef4faa60419196e19c798f032484" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2082ef4faa60419196e19c798f032484}" title="Hotel La Torre">Hotel La Torre</a>, where guests can use the spa facilities for <span>€</span><span>20. These include a jacuzzi, sensory showers, sauna, steam room and gym.</span></p>
<h3>Igloo bubbles</h3>
<p>If you're looking for an après experience with a bit of winter magic, the Hotel K2 has two unique bubble igloos. You can enjoy aperitivos and a glass of wine in your private igloo whilst snow falls around you, payable locally.</p>]]></description>
